<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This type defines a spherical shape. The origin is at the center of the sphere.</db:para>
<db:note>
<db:para>When using a scaling transformation with this shape, the x component will be used to scale the diameter of the sphere. The resulting shape will be perfectly round, even if a non-uniform scaling transformation is used.</db:para>
</db:note>
</db:section>
